<h5 id="arg-unknown-option" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#arg-unknown-option" aria-hidden="true">#</a> ARG_UNKNOWN_OPTION</h5>
<p>If an unknown option (not defined in the spec object) is passed, an error with code <code v-pre>ARG_UNKNOWN_OPTION</code> will be thrown:</p>
